      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s looking for a brand-new home. It\u2019s been so well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip! It's in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how smooth it handles. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
