    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. The powerplant maintains excellent compression and crisp throttle response across the rev range, aided by a properly calibrated double-VANOS system. Power is sent through a 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction out of corners. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to maintain structural rigidity. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, preserving the communicative chassis dynamics this platform is known for. While it displays honest signs of road use, the drivetrain and critical mechanical components are in robust health for the dedicated driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
