    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of its model year. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster with only minor road peppering on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features supple leather seats with minimal bolstering wear, while all electronics and climate controls function perfectly. Mechanically, it is robust; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and it sits on a set of premium tires with significant tread remaining. Complete service records are available, documenting regular oil changes and recent brake service. It\u2019s a reliable, high-performing driver\u2019s car that looks sharp and feels even better on the road.",
      "price": 34800.0,
