    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for its mechanical consistency and well-preserved condition. Rigorously inspected by our senior technicians, it offers a sophisticated driving experience and remains a testament to diligent previous ownership. This is a definitive choice for those seeking reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 34500.0,
