    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner right away! It's super reliable and perfect for both daily commutes and fun weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll feel the love the moment you hop in. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
