    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving heritage. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for an 8,000 RPM redline. The power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone critical preventive maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system overhaul. The suspension retains its precise geometry with updated bushings, ensuring the chassis remains communicative and balanced. A driver-focused machine with sorted internals and a linear power band.",
